## User SignIn [/users/signin]

This action allows you to signin to your account.

### Authenticate User [POST]

You may signin to your account using this action. It takes a JSON object containing user details.

+ email (required, unique, string) - The user's email address.
+ password (required, string) - The user's password.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "email": "iverenshaguy@gmail.com",
            "password": "iverenshaguy"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /users/1
    
    + Body

