## Group Favorite Recipe

Resources related to favorite recipes.

## Add Favorite Recipe [/recipes/{recipeId}/favorites]

This action allows you add a recipe to your favorites.

+ Parameters
    + recipeId: 9 (required, number) - ID of the Recipe to add to favorites in form of an integer.

### Add Recipe to Favorites [POST]

You may add a recipe tp your favorite recipes using this action. It takes no input.

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /recipes/9/favorites/1
    
    + Body

            {
                "id": 1,
                "favorite": true,
                "recipeId": 9,
                "userId": 1
            }


